## ğŸ§  Bot API Overview

A CTOR bot is a JavaScript function:

```js
export function myBot(board, color) {
  return { row: Number, col: Number };
}
```

Where:

| Parameter | Description |
|----------|-------------|
| `board` | 8Ã—8 array with `"R"`, `"B"`, `"."` |
| `color` | `"R"` or `"B"` |
| return | `{ row, col }` â€” your chosen move |

If the bot returns an illegal move â†’ it loses automatically.

